# conv_HWC_s8_s8_s8_RGB_sft_bias

## What This Function Does

Convolution for RGB (3-channel) input tensors with shift-based (sft) quantization. No channel alignment constraint (unlike the _fast variant). Test shape: in_dim=23, out_ch=26, ker=3, in_ch=3, K=27, pad=0, stride=1.

## Active Code Path (AX45MPV)

`#if defined(ENA_TILING) && (NDS_VEC_RVV_VERSION >= 1000)` inside `#elif defined(ENA_VEC_ISA)`.

Direct convolution using VQMACC (vectorize N), no im2col. Ported from `RGB_sft_bias_fast`.

